description.en: ROBODOGE is the very first ""fluid"" tokenomic model designed to prevent panic selling through smart AI software. This project has been in the making for almost a year now. The founder is a 17 year trading veteran. ROBODOGE has successfully produced a brand new model that has never been seen before. The model is aimed to prevent panic selling, bot pump and dumps, and tackling the root of the issue, ""the fear"" driving the panic. ROBODOGE uses a smart AI system, and a very unique EOP ""ease out protocol"" to deliver the very first responsible trading system. ROBODOGE has brought a little Wall Street sophistication into the crypto space.
